00:40:22,787 --> 00:40:24,152
Stop it!

420
00:40:33,764 --> 00:40:35,823
You killed him with one blow.

421
00:40:37,067 --> 00:40:38,227
I...

422
00:40:38,335 --> 00:40:40,394
Wait.

423
00:40:40,504 --> 00:40:41,698
I understood you.

424
00:40:43,641 --> 00:40:45,700
